Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.21,0:00:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.15,0:00:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.99,0:00:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.46,0:00:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.54,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.68,0:00:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.02,0:00:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.93,0:01:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.17,0:01:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.25,0:01:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.49,0:01:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嚇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.71,0:02:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,謝謝您平時的關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,空房間是有\N現在就要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.44,0:02:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.84,0:02:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.59,0:03:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,如果你要去一刻館的話\N應該往反方向走才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.22,0:03:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是這樣嗎?,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像要下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.67,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#50 響子一見鍾情?!\N一刻館出現奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人要搬進來住嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.92,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都好,總之要開歡迎會才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代你在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,衣服還沒收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要買點下酒菜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,順便去一下茶茶丸\N通知朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我打電話給她好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還沒來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.49,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N不過行李已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是害怕所以溜掉了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何聯絡,真的蠻奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果撲了一個空啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.24,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊,從五代之後\N就沒有房客住進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.51,0:05:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說,又不是真的不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯還沒吃吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這次搬進來這裡住的\N我叫三越善三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為下雨的關係所以來晚了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,他是那麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他一整晚怎麼度過的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個小道消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有新的房客住進來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人看起來\N絕對不會變成你的情敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.24,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼情敵\N真討厭,我才沒有在想這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,我也只是隨便問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實在意的要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三越先生也會打網球嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紙箱子只有一個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,他的東西好像只有那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好特別的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看他是個怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.64,0:07:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個人住進一刻館\N而你也一直住在一刻館的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我們會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.91,0:08:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興喔\N一刻館變得熱鬧是件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊,儘量喝儘量喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊\N喝醉了大家會照顧你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要可是了啦\N來,喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,一口氣乾掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖乖聽這些人的話去做\N下場會很淒慘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個袖子是不是太長了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N相對的,下擺就有點短了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.71,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很喜歡這件衣服\N穿到這樣還在穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.35,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是你過世的老婆\N親手幫你縫製的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.29,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思\N我本來只是隨便說說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.06,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,請不要放在心上\N那已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,妳怎麼沒跳舞呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.18,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本都沒喝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員也喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N今天我也豁出去來喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人豁出去的時候\N經常很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事幹嘛問我啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了,喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡情的喝!盡情的喝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,乖喔乖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃這個啊,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,把你褲子弄得髒髒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.44,0:10:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是我有波蘿麵包\N妳要不要吃一點啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蘿麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我本來想吃甜食的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒買到甜食嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,店家說他們沒有賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.16,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給妳,我沒有什麼食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像不太適合喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡住的都是一些好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個好天氣,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,還有牛奶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我這個人很懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來幫你縫吧\N當作是麵包的謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N這樣我反而會不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說,把你褲子弄髒了\N我才不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個坐在門口幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真的好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說哪裡特別像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是整個人的感覺很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.20,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香港腳不趁現在治好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等天氣暖和了就更麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.41,0:13:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,不好意思,請問你叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.51,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姓四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷菊千代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.75,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不,雖然寫成菊千代\N不過,要唸成“為藏”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.82,0:13:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫我“親切的阿為”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是下班要回家啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.40,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.24,0:13:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種溫暖的好天氣\N去上班就太沒趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你也是這麼想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你在一刻館住很久了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經久到無法計算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想搬到別的地方去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人還真壞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.13,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你,在那麼多公寓裡\N你為什麼獨獨選擇了一刻館呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是氣息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被溫暖的春天氣息吸引來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三越先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才跟四谷在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,他找我來吃蕎麥麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是四谷付錢的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有超市嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要買東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我想買個小鍋子和水壺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼的話\N去車站前的五金行買比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?我們衝過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是管理員和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.82,0:15:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快點啦,要開始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,滿出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,真的不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,會留下痕跡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員真是個好太太型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,人家才跟妳不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.25,0:16:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在興奮什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,沒事\N給我啤酒,啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我來跳一段舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.22,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?\N你的表情怎麼比平常更灰暗了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟音無小姐之間\N出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼,討人厭的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對了,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.04,0:17:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…我問你\N新搬進來的那個房客怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.70,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,算了,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.04,0:18:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻館的人\N總讓我覺得好像是一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.64,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒有人會追問我的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.95,0:18:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像已經住在一起很久似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的讓我覺得很奇妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.82,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也覺得非常高興,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,惣一郎,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉\N我沒有帶東西回來給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們一起去的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,碰巧遇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧,我煮了一些甜酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒說錯吧\N-是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們進去喝甜酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請,可是我不敢保證好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會不好喝呢\N既然是管理員做的甜酒一定好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?很像嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說整個人的感覺很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.76,0:19:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直猶豫要不要跟你講呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也稍微察覺到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.91,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想,搞不好他會變成\N比三鷹還強的情敵喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在對方身上\N感覺得到惣一郎的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這對手就太強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.72,0:20:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你也別硬要跟他競爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時觀察一陣子再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曬太陽取暖\N妳要不要也一起來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.24,0:20:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三越先生,你要出門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後電風扇的開關一開\N一隻被切成塵屑的蟑螂飛了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果跑進鼻子裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.03,0:21:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後用力吐了一口氣\N蟑螂居然從嘴巴裡跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我在想一些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你好可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然那個傳聞是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.26,0:21:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐好有精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼認為啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說也?這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛大驚小怪的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.87,0:21:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,不要隱瞞\N把一切告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傳聞是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?妳不知道嗎?\N大家都在說耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說我們店裡的常客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.89,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,連妳都不知道的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.06,0:22:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定只是空穴來風的八卦謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是上班時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N我聽到一件很奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是剛剛才聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.85,0:22:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.15,0:22:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳聽到的是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說一刻館要被拆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽到的都是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.23,0:22:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.33,0:22:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是三鷹自己加油添醋的臆測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.66,0:22:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說管理員要再婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.70,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.33,0:22:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那麼回事\N我才沒有要再婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.30,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹個性就是這麼急躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.61,0:22:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這也太奇怪了\N我們這些房客明明都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.78,0:22:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.98,0:22:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,今天還沒有見到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是四谷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.09,0:23:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.73,0:23:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三越先生,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.90,0:23:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好,好像快要下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代你呢?喝啤酒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.87,0:23:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.70,0:23:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,妳冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.07,0:23:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小津江不是說她看見了\N三越他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「四谷也震驚不已!\N一刻館消失的日子?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.71,0:24:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著這天到來的人,只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.38,0:24:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.19,0:24:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.83,0:24:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.44,0:24:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.38,0:24:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.89,0:24:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.29,0:24:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.00,0:24:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.87,0:25:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.07,0:25:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.08,0:25:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.19,0:25:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.19,0:25:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
